{
  "stem": "10588.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But what I remember most is that it was completely because of the inconveniences of lacking the things, which I said, the modern things, my mother and grandmother-- may they rest in peace-- used to buy beets.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And before the, before the holiday, so like a month before, make beets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Buy raisin, make their own raisin wine, because it was strictly kosher in our home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Prepare.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we used to go, you know, in a, in a pillow case we would put in and go bring the matza-- a special pillow case.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was not a pillow case that you slept, but, like, it looked like a pillow case.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Bring home the matza for, for yuntif.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And at the seder, I used to love the way they did the seder.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And-- but to tell you the truth, if every year we prayed, next year in Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But the point is, to me, it was like a story.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I believed it, but I, I was still fortunate that I still had a family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I never knew what hunger was, because I wasn't 13 years-- I was 13 when the war started.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So till 13, I didn't fast for Yom Kippur, so I didn't know what hunger is, you know, because I haven't experienced it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a story with all the plagues, with all the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So till-- and later on, I was thinking, when I was-- during the Holocaust, realizing that now I know it's not just a story.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now I experienced far worse than what it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Another thing which I loved that my parents used to take me to the Yiddish theater.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I mentioned before, my mother would only give a performance occasionally.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What type?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Yiddish theater.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
